@startuml sequence_authenticated_request
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Authenticated Request — Common Path (Both Auth Modes)

actor Caller
participant "API Endpoint" as API
participant "JwtBearer\nMiddleware" as JWT
participant "UserBootstrap\nHandler" as Boot
participant "ICurrentUser" as CU
participant "MediatR Handler" as MR
database "user table" as DB

Caller -> API: GET /api/tree\nBearer <jwt>
API -> JWT: Authenticate
JWT -> JWT: Validate token
JWT -> Boot: OnTokenValidated
Boot -> DB: SELECT user WHERE email=@e
DB --> Boot: User
Boot -> CU: Set UserId, Email
Boot --> JWT: ok
JWT --> API: ClaimsPrincipal
API -> MR: Send(request)
note right of MR
  Today: handler ignores
  CurrentUser. Future
  ownership work injects
  ICurrentUser here.
end note
MR --> API: response
API --> Caller: 200 OK

@enduml
